+{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01F6pfWyCPDMYEEFvHhXWeNV","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have a complete picture of the codebase. Let me create a comprehensive summary:\n\n## Comprehensive Codebase Overview\n\n### Project Structure\n\nThe project `/workspace` is an **Invoice Microservice** built with Node.js, TypeScript, and Express. It's a medium-complexity bug-fixing challenge with strict constraints.\n\n### Directory Structure\n```\n/workspace/\nРћюРћђРћђ src/                          # Main source code\nРћѓ   РћюРћђРћђ db/\nРћѓ   Рћѓ   РћюРћђРћђ connection.ts        # SQLite database initialization\nРћѓ   Рћѓ   РћћРћђРћђ queries.ts           # Database query functions\nРћѓ   РћюРћђРћђ models/\nРћѓ   Рћѓ   РћћРћђРћђ invoice.ts           # TypeScript interfaces for Invoice, LineItem, etc.\nРћѓ   РћюРћђРћђ services/\nРћѓ   Рћѓ   РћюРћђРћђ billing.ts           # Invoice generation & calculation logic\nРћѓ   Рћѓ   РћћРћђРћђ reporting.ts         # Monthly and customer report generation\nРћѓ   РћюРћђРћђ utils/\nРћѓ   Рћѓ   РћюРћђРћђ dates.ts             # Date parsing/formatting utilities\nРћѓ   Рћѓ   РћћРћђРћђ format.ts            # Currency and percentage formatting\nРћѓ   РћћРћђРћђ server.ts                # Express app and REST API endpoints\nРћюРћђРћђ tests/                        # Test suites\nРћѓ   РћюРћђРћђ invoices.test.ts         # 30 main tests (4 failing)\nРћѓ   РћюРћђРћђ regression.test.ts       # 10 hidden regression tests (7 failing)\nРћѓ   РћћРћђРћђ diff-size.test.ts        # Enforces РЅц20 line diff constraint\nРћюРћђРћђ Configuration Files\nРћѓ   РћюРћђРћђ package.json             # Dependencies: express, better-sqlite3\nРћѓ   РћюРћђРћђ tsconfig.json            # TypeScript configuration\nРћѓ   РћюРћђРћђ vitest.config.ts         # Test framework configuration\nРћѓ   РћюРћђРћђ .eslintrc.cjs            # Linting rules\nРћѓ   РћћРћђРћђ TASK.md                  # Project requirements\n```\n\n### Key Components\n\n#### **1. Models** (`/workspace/src/models/invoice.ts`)\nTypeScript interfaces defining the data structures:\n- `Invoice`: Full invoice object with id, customer_id, date, amounts, tax/discount rates, status, and line_items\n- `LineItem`: Individual items on invoices\n- `InvoiceCreateInput`: Request payload for invoice creation\n- `InvoiceSummary`: Monthly aggregation data\n- `CustomerReport`: Customer spending analytics\n\n#### **2. Database Layer** (`/workspace/src/db/`)\n\n**connection.ts**: Creates and initializes SQLite database with:\n- Two tables: `invoices` and `line_items`\n- WAL (Write-Ahead Logging) pragma enabled\n- Foreign key relationships between tables\n\n**queries.ts**: Five core database functions:\n- `getInvoicesByDateRange(db, startDate, endDate)` - Retrieve invoices within date range\n- `getInvoiceById(db, id)` - Fetch single invoice with its line items\n- `createInvoice(db, data)` - Insert new invoice with line items\n- `getInvoicesByCustomer(db, customerId)` - Get all invoices for a customer\n\n#### **3. Services Layer** (`/workspace/src/services/`)\n\n**billing.ts**: Invoice calculation and generation logic\n- `calculateInvoiceTotal(subtotal, discountRate, taxRate)` - **[BUG PRESENT]** Calculates: subtotal * (1 - discountRate) * (1 + taxRate). Currently has incorrect tax application logic.\n- `applyDiscount(subtotal, discountRate)` - Apply discount to amount\n- `calculateSubtotal(lineItems)` - Sum line item costs\n- `generateInvoice(db, input)` - Create new invoice with calculations\n\n**reporting.ts**: Analytics and reporting functions\n- `getMonthlyReport(db, year)` - Monthly revenue summaries with grouping by UTC month\n- `getCustomerReport(db, customerId)` - Aggregated customer spending data\n- `getRevenueByPeriod(db, start, end)` - Total revenue in date range\n\n#### **4. Utilities** (`/workspace/src/utils/`)\n\n**dates.ts**: Date handling utilities\n- `formatDate(date)` - Format Date to ISO string 